DEADCELLS-MAGNIFICENT_CARD_BG.hover.desc:
When [gold]enabled[/gold], card backgrounds will be set according to the [gold]attribute classification[/gold] of weapons in the original [gold]Dead Cells[/gold] game by default.
When [gold]disabled[/gold], background colors are determined by card type:
[red]Attack[/red] Cards: Red;
[purple]Skill[/purple] Cards: Purple;
[green]Power[/green] Cards: Green;
All other cards: Gray.
